And yet so many of these great ladies in the
Paris story are dancers, singers, chorus-girls ;
all blended together, as in life, I suppose;
journalists, singers, bankers, painters and girls ;
an odd crew.... and all so real.
One wonders, is the whole book a libel,
or is it true ?... or is it mezzo e mezzo.

